headline: Has Dell’s AI Infrastructure Push Left Further Upside for Investors in 2025?
summary: If you are wondering whether Dell Technologies still offers value after a strong run, or if most of the easy gains may already be behind it, this breakdown can help you assess whether the current price still appears attractive. Despite a modest pullback of around 2.7% over the past week, Dell is still up roughly 3.2% over the last month, 8.5% year to date, and 273.5% over five years.
